so it's impossible
at this time to know...

01:29:24.375 --> 01:29:26.775
how many unaffected people
are left.

01:29:26.810 --> 01:29:29.938
If for any reason...

01:29:29.980 --> 01:29:32.972
you are one of us
who hasn't become infected...

01:29:33.017 --> 01:29:34.746
take shelter immediately.

01:29:34.785 --> 01:29:36.776
Do not trust any friends
or family members.

01:29:36.820 --> 01:29:39.880
