It was a lucky shot, that's all!

01:29:51.869 --> 01:29:53.393
What?!

01:29:53.437 --> 01:29:55.769
I am not insane.

01:29:55.806 --> 01:29:59.264
Do you hear me?
I am not insane!

01:30:02.446 --> 01:30:05.415
Relax, buddy.
You're awake now.

